author: COMSOL
description: This model is a version of the Structural Mechanics Module tutorial model of a bracket with a fully parameterized geometry. A series of uncertainty quantification studies is run to assess which geometric parameters influence the pin hole angle the most and what the probability is that the pin hole angle exceeds 0.1 degree.
label: bracket_uncertainty_quantification.mph
